data.description: Step into luxury with this immaculate, essentially brand-new home boasting modern design and high-end finishes. Revel in the elegance of LVP flooring, granite countertops, and sleek stainless steel appliances in the kitchen. With 4 bedrooms and 2 baths, this residence provides ample space for comfort and convenience. The 2-car garage and dedicated laundry room add practicality to the seamless blend of style and functionality. Enjoy the perfect balance of indoor and outdoor living with a covered back patio, creating an ideal space for morning coffees or evening gatherings. The home has been professionally cleaned and is turn key and move in ready. Welcome to your dream home!
